reviewText: Loved them all these years, and the farewell presentatin brought tears to our eyes....we truly love their signing and am happy that the young boys are taking over the part that will be missed forever.....but they have the right handle on things, and we'll be enjoying them over and over again.  Thanks...Farewell....and Welcome to the Newcomers.

reviewText: I saw this group sing in concert several times.  On a wide HDTV it is like being at a concert with them.  All the favorites were sung.  I usually fast forward past the talking which gets old.  But the singing never will.
